Date: ${date}

SELLER INFORMATION:
Name: NextSelf
Email: app.nextself@gmail.com
Service Type: Digital Fitness (SaaS) and Remote Education/Consultancy

BUYER INFORMATION:
Full Name: ${buyerName}
Email: ${buyerEmail}
Address: ${buyerAddress || 'Not specified'}

CONTRACT SUBJECT:
